    <item>
      <title>2023 年最佳短线电话属于业余“脏泡泡”侦探</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/best-short-call-of-2023-belongs-to-amateur-dirty-bubble-sleuth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年最好的做空决定不是由一家无情的对冲基金、一家知名的激进公司或任何卖方最活跃的声音做出的。它是由一位一年级住院医师制作的，他经营着一个以海绵宝宝角色命名的博客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/best-short-call-of-2023-belongs-to-amateur-dirty-bubble-sleuth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 11:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行拉加德：“攻击”是应对特朗普第二任期的最佳防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-19/lagarde-attack-is-best-defense-against-a-trump-return-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“如果我们这么看的话，最好的防守就是进攻。”欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德解释了支持欧洲单一市场是为唐纳德·特朗普可能在 2025 年重返白宫做准备的最佳计划。拉加德在瑞士达沃斯世界经济论坛年会上的一个小组会议上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-19/lagarde-attack-is-best-defense-against-a-trump-return-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 10:49:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国通胀冲击使英国国债迎来有史以来最糟糕的一年开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/uk-inflation-jump-is-a-warning-to-market-dead-set-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀意外飙升促使投资者重新考虑英国央行可以降息多少之后，英国债券延续了今年主要市场的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/uk-inflation-jump-is-a-warning-to-market-dead-set-on-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 10:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华印度公司利润因需求疲软而未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/unilever-india-profit-misses-expectations-on-rising-competition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度消费品巨头印度斯坦联合利华有限公司 (Hindustan Unilever Ltd.) 公布的季度利润令人失望，原因是该公司面临需求疲软、节日淡季以及竞争对手蚕食该公司市场份额的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/unilever-india-profit-misses-expectations-on-rising-competition</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 10:15:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国新增外资跌至三年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/new-foreign-investment-into-china-drops-to-lowest-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于香港和海外企业不太愿意将新资金投入内地，去年流入中国的新增外国直接投资跌至三年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/new-foreign-investment-into-china-drops-to-lowest-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 09:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华融评级降至垃圾级，穆迪下调中国坏账银行评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/chinese-bad-debt-manager-huarong-downgraded-to-junk-by-moody-s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对房地产危机的担忧，穆迪投资者服务公司将中国最大的坏账管理公司的评级下调，将中国华融资产管理公司的评级降至垃圾级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/chinese-bad-debt-manager-huarong-downgraded-to-junk-by-moody-s</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 08:24:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>价值 210 亿美元的印度银行股暴跌预示着全盛时期可能已经结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/a-21-billion-rout-in-india-s-banks-signal-best-days-maybe-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度最大的私营银行 HDFC Bank Ltd. 罕见遭到抛售后，价值 4,330 亿美元的印度银行业前景迅速恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/a-21-billion-rout-in-india-s-banks-signal-best-days-maybe-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 05:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
